"{\"uid\": \"espn.com-olympics-skiing-story-_-id-39582440-biathlon-president-investigation-austria\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"SALZBURG, Austria -- The governing body for the Winter Olympic sport of biathlon has confirmed its president Olle Dahlin is under investigation by Austrian authorities.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salzburg\", \"score\": 0.9999989063839234, \"rank\": 4.6360241610891554e-07, \"text\": \"SALZBURG\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salzburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salzburg\"}, {\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9998964178620372, \"rank\": 8.571288110453052e-05, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9985889597988007, \"rank\": 0.0010965749120213162, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The governing body\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 39}, {\"ngram\": \"the Winter Olympic sport\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 68}, {\"ngram\": \"biathlon\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 80}, {\"ngram\": \"its president\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"Olle Dahlin\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 120}, {\"ngram\": \"investigation\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, its former president Anders Besseberg is awaiting a verdict in an alleged corruption trial in Norway.\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999958972559887, \"rank\": 3.547657619360364e-06, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"its former president\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 208}, {\"ngram\": \"Anders Besseberg\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 225}, {\"ngram\": \"a verdict\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"an alleged corruption trial\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Biathlon Union said in an e-mailed statement that it \\\"is aware of the Austrian authorities' investigation into the IBU President\\\" but would not comment on details.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Biathlon Union\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999973563768364, \"rank\": 1.0932972588685893e-06, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9985889597988007, \"rank\": 0.0010965749120213162, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999940681801436, \"rank\": 5.93185497445984e-06, \"text\": \"IBU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an e-mailed statement\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have not received any formal notification of any investigation at this stage, but I am aware of politically motivated speculation and innuendos.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any formal notification\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"any investigation\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"this stage\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"politically motivated speculation\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"innuendos\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am totally shocked by these allegations which are completely without foundation, and I refute them all in the strongest possible terms.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these allegations\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"foundation\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"the strongest possible terms\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will not hesitate to take any legal action necessary to uphold my good name and reputation,\\\" Dahlin said in a statement released by the IBU.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999940681801436, \"rank\": 5.93185497445984e-06, \"text\": \"IBU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any legal action\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"my good name\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"reputation\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"Dahlin\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While I deny wrongdoing of any kind, I will ensure my total cooperation and have complete confidence that the investigation will find I have no case to answer.\\\"\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wrongdoing\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"my total cooperation\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"complete confidence\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigation\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"no case\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dahlin did not comment on the detail of the investigation but defended the IBU's handling of its marketing arrangements.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999940681801436, \"rank\": 5.93185497445984e-06, \"text\": \"IBU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dahlin\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the detail\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigation\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1124}, {\"ngram\": \"its marketing arrangements\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The process for the latest IBU marketing contract was implemented in full compliance with the IBU's Integrity Code and due diligence was undertaken to ensure that it was appropriate and in accordance with industry norms,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Biathlon_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999940681801436, \"rank\": 5.93185497445984e-06, \"text\": \"IBU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.